title: Todd Mackey from With Honor
itunes:title: Todd Mackey from With Honor
description:
What a treat this week as we have my friend Todd Mackey from With Honor on the podcast. They recently signed with Pure Noise Records and are in the process of getting some new music ready for 2022. We go in depth about faith, open heartedness and his life after the band in the donut trade (seriously).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
